    <item>
      <title>Stifel 的 Kruszewski 表示并购环境正在改善</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-25/stifel-s-kruszewski-says-m-a-environment-is-improving</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Stifel 董事长兼首席执行官 Ron Kruszewski 表示，为交易提供咨询的环境正在改善。他表示，美国的通胀具有粘性，美联储不应急于降息。他在“彭博监视”节目中发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-25/stifel-s-kruszewski-says-m-a-environment-is-improving</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 13:40:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Permira 首席执行官预计私募股权公司将面临高利率冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/permira-chief-sees-private-equity-shakeout-with-rates-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[私募股权行业正面临一场清算——借贷成本高企，投资组合公司的估值下降，投资者的要求越来越高。但对于佩米拉的顶头上司来说，情况还算不错。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/permira-chief-sees-private-equity-shakeout-with-rates-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 13:14:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚航计划斥资 14 亿美元合并新股</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/airasia-plans-new-listing-with-1-4-billion-merger-of-units</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲航空宣布斥资 68 亿林吉特（14.2 亿美元）创建一个新的上市实体，该实体将通过合并其各个航空公司部门来简化其运营。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/airasia-plans-new-listing-with-1-4-billion-merger-of-units</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 13:03:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
