      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 12:43:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡特彼勒第二季度销售放缓警告后股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/caterpillar-profit-beats-estimates-as-pricing-offsets-sales-dip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡特彼勒公司公布的第一季度业绩显示，机械销量较上年同期下滑，并警告称，预计第二季度这一趋势将持续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/caterpillar-profit-beats-estimates-as-pricing-offsets-sales-dip</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 10:37:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿德勒（Adler）减价出售失败，债权人将接管公司控制权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/german-real-estate-firm-adler-reaches-agreement-with-bondholders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在房价暴跌的背景下，陷入困境的房东难以出售资产和偿还债务，阿德勒集团 (Adler Group SA) 的债权人将接管该公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/german-real-estate-firm-adler-reaches-agreement-with-bondholders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 09:34:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
